{
  "stem": "8703.7",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I started plumbing.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And, and I made a living, you know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And at that time-- that time right after I came, two weeks after I joined the Jewish underground there, the Irgun.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And after a month, about two months, I joined them.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "It was in April.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And June, the beginning of June, we had to join the Jewish [NON-ENGLISH], the Jewish army.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "In June, I joined the army and all the members from Irgun joined the army at that time.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And I was, well, that time we all-- it was the War of Independence.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And I was in the army also close to a year and a half.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And after the army, I started to work, like I said before, plumbing.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And I supported myself.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "It was very, very rough times.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the army, I was in the-- in the technician's army.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And, and my brother started to write to me and send some packages also, and help me.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because food was over there, even after the creation of the Jewish state, was very, very rough to get at that time.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We had the wars, one after the other at that time.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It started the war.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Then it stopped.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he once, he asked me to come-- not to come-- to go to the United States.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But he knew that I wouldn't go because I liked Israel, you know?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It's the first time that I was a free man when I came to Israel.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I joined the army.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I really considered myself as a free man, and I wanted-- and I could, you know, contribute something to the creation of the Jewish state.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And he asked me if I would come for a visit to the United States.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I said, yes.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
